return 'Manage your data views easily:
• **Show/hide columns** using the column visibility controls
• **Save custom views** with your preferred column setup
• **Switch between saved views** using the view selector
• Views are automatically saved to your browser.';

return 'The Revenue & FTE tab helps with workforce calculations:
• Upload **leave data** and **people data** files
• Calculates **FTE (Full Time Equivalent)** metrics
• Processes **revenue calculations** based on working days
• Supports **multi-file analysis** for comprehensive reporting.';

return 'The app includes UK working days calculations:
• **Excludes weekends** (Saturday & Sunday)
• **Excludes UK public holidays** for England & Wales
• Used in Revenue & FTE calculations
• Based on official UK government holiday calendar.';

